                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Hands on tour through Eclipse 2!!! Plugin Development</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
